Package com.intellij.openapi.util

Class SystemInfoRt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.util.SystemInfoRt

  • public final class SystemInfoRt
extends java.lang.Object
    A stripped-down version of SystemInfo. Intended to use by external (out-of-IDE-process) runners and helpers so it should not contain any library dependencies.
